Subject: Narrative Subject File Table

Description: Seed table mapping narrated subject matters to files of interest for local SOP re-entry.

@ [source] C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\platform\NarrativeSubjectFileIndex.sop
@ [source] C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\platform\attention_layers\NarrativeDigestion.sop

& [NarrativeSubjectFileTable] is the current table for narrative-subject file interests
  + [table_status] is seed
  + [table_scope] is active attention, narrative digestion, runtime registry, surface inquiry, and semantic re-entry subjects
  + [authority_root] is C:\Project\Pinky\.sop
  + [subject_count] is 8
  + [coverage_status] is partial and intentionally non-exhaustive
  + [residual_outside] is unindexed narrative subjects, stale historical F:\.sop paths, runtime-only details, and subjects not yet reviewed

  = must: support lookup by narrative_subject_key
  = must: preserve relation reasons and depth hints
  = must: keep table entries as re-entry guidance rather than authority
  = should: be expanded when narrative digestion promotes a subject into durable SOP
  - never: treat this table as complete coverage of the repository

& [Subject_narrative_subject_file_index] is a narrative subject entry
  + [subject_key] is narrative_subject_file_index
  + [narrative_surface] is C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\platform\source_documents\2026-06-24_narrative_subject_file_index\Dictated_Narrative_Subject_File_Index_Source.sop
  + [file_interest_set] is C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\platform\NarrativeSubjectFileIndex.sop, C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\platform\indexes\NarrativeSubjectFileTable.sop, C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\platform\attention_layers\NarrativeDigestion.sop, C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\platform\SurfacePeripheryInquiryIndex.sop, C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\state\CurrentFocalPoint.sop, and C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\state\AttentionRuntimeRegistryState.sop
  + [relation_reason_set] is canonical contract, seed table, narrative layer integration, surface lookup bridge, current focus state, and semantic stack-frame state
  + [search_phrase_set] is narrative_subject_key, file_of_interest, file_interest_relation, subject_file_table, NarrativeSubjectFileIndex, NarrativeSubjectFileTable
  + [depth_hint] is impact
  + [coverage_status] is seed
  + [outside] is complete repository map or proof that every relevant file has been indexed

